@imwithherband is the epitome of the @newportfolkfest spirit of collaboration. Three equally magnificent talents joining together to make an indelible mark in the lexicon of folk music. @aoifemaria and @sarawatkins will be around the fort this year, so who knows what might happen (here’s looking at you @sarahjarosz ). That’s the beauty of this festival. #roadtonewport #newportfolkfest #imwithher #aoifeodonovan #sarawatkins #sarahjarosz #joshwool #music

@goosetheband @carm_band and @steadycraig running through a song before taking the quad stage at Newport Folk Festival last year. A day with Corey Wheeler Forrest at her commercial fishing operation in Little Compton, Rhode Island. Corey and her fellow independent commercial fishermen are fighting to preserve a generations old industry amidst challenging economic and environmental conditions. Sustainability is at the heart of her operation and it’s important to support these small farmers and fisherman who work so hard to put food on our tables in responsible, ethical ways. #commercialfishing #sustainability #smallbusiness #coreywheelerforrest #joshwool #leica #documentaryphotography #rhodeisland #xtratuf
